quran[21{c,v,t}:
54,7,log sehmi hui nigahon ke sath apni qabron se iss terhan nikleen ge goya woh bhikri hui tidyan hain
54,8,pukarnay walay ki taraf doray ja rahay hon ge aur wohi munkareen ( jo duniya mein is ka inkaar karte thay ) uss waqt kahin ge ke yeh din to bara kathin hai
54,9,"inn se pehlay Nooh ki qoum jhutla chuki hai onhon ne hamaray bande ko jhoota qarar diya aur kaha ke yeh deewana hai, aur woh buri terhanjihrkagaya"
54,10,"aakhir-kaar uss ne apne rab ko puraka ke"" mein maghloob ho chuka, ab to inn se intiqam le """
54,11,tab hum ne mosla dhaar barish se aasman ke darwazay khol diye aur zameen ko phaar kar chashmon mein tabdeel kar diya
54,12,aur yeh sara pani uss kaam ko poora karne liye mil gaya jo muqaddar ho chuka tha
54,13,aur Nooh ko hum ne aik takhton aur kilon wali par sawaar kar diya
54,14,jo hamari nigrani mein chal rahi thi yeh tha badla uss shakhs ki khatir jis ki na qadri ki gayi thi
54,15,"uss kashti ko hum ne aik nishani bana kar chore diya, phir koi hai nasiyaat qubool karne wala ?"
54,16,"dekh lau, kaisa tha mera azaab aur kaisi theen meri tnbihat"
54,17,"hum ne iss quran ko nasiyaat ke liye aasaan zareya bana diya hai, phir kya hai koi nasiyaat qubool karne wala ?"
54,18,"Aad ne jhtlaya, to dekh lau ke kaisa tha mera azaab aur kaisi theen meri tnbihat"
54,19,hum ne aik pihm nahosat ke din sakht tofani howa unn par bhaij di jo logon ko utha utha kar is terhan pheink rahi thi
54,20,jaisay woh jarr se akhrhe hue khajoor ke tanay hon
54,21,pas dekh lau ke kaisa tha mera azaab aur kaisi theen meri tnbihat
54,22,"hum ne iss quran ko nasiyaat ke liye aasaan zareya bana diya hai, phir kya hai koi nasiyaat qubool karne wala ?"
54,23,samood ne tnbihat ko jhtlaya
54,24,"aur kehnay lagey"" aik akela aadmi jo hum hi mein se hai kya ab hum uss ke peechay chalein? iss ka itebaa hum qubool kar len to iss ke maienay yeh hon ge ke hum behak gay hain aur hamari aqal maari gayi hai"
54,25,"kya hamaray darmain bas yahishakhs tha jis par khuda ka zikar nazil kya gaya? nahi, balkay yeh parlay darjay ka jhoota aur Bar khud ghalat hai """
54,26,"( hum ne apne paighambar se kaha )"" kal hi aِnhin maloom howa jata hai ke kon parlay darjay ka jhoota aur Bar khud ghalat hai"
54,27,hum oontni ko inn ke liye fitnah bana kar bhaij rahay hain ab zara sabr ke sath dekh ke inn ka kya injaam hota hai
